  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Anyway, there came a time where we knew that, or at least my sister at that time, was rebelling and was answering them back to a point that one day they actually shoved her out of the house and said well, be found out and be killed.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're a Jew, and if you do this again this is exactly where you and your family will be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was thrown out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they, I think with some reasoning, and the realization that whether they were getting money or their purposes were, that hiding Jews, whether for money or not for money, was a penalty of death, they decided to let her back in.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we knew then, because of the fact that my sister was maybe not as young as I was, so I was able to take a lot more.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the fact that they were using and abusing her a lot more than they were doing to me, that it-- it would have been impossible for her to stay there because this would have happened again and, of course, if she's discovered we would be discovered.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my sister was-- was six years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So at the time I would say she was 13, 14, and certainly able to understand a lot more of what was happening to us than I was.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Although I was growing up very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] At this point I'm dark on how we were able to contact the underground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I would assume it [? was the ?] Barniche, because they saw that she was becoming impossible to deal with, and very rebellious.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the underground was contacted, and my sister was taken out of there and taken to a convent.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
